item.title: Everything is so confusing.
item.description: So work got hard again. everyone is super stressed and really getting down about this project. I am confident it will be resolved soon enough. we just have to do it ;)in the meantime, we shoudl all be playing NES and then download GTA and go killin. this is incredibly strange. I really don’t understand what it is. happy sabrina?? this isn’t as weird.. but is very strange. good thing I use the e2cs.
